Introduction

NEXZ is a global group under JYP Entertainment, formed through the survival show "Nizi Project Season 2." The group's members include Yu, Tomoya, Haru, So Geon, Seita, Hyui, and Yuki. The group's name stands for "Next Z(G)eneration."

NEXZ debuted with their single album, "Ride the Vibe," on May 20, 2024. Prior to their official debut, they began their pre-debut activities on December 18, 2023, with the release of the Japanese and Korean versions of their digital single "Miracle."
